articles.title: monday.com (MNDY) Q1 2025 Earnings Call Transcript
articles.summary: Motley Fool: monday.com (MNDY) Q1 2025 Earnings Call Transcript. Roy Mann: Thank you, Byron, and thank you, everyone for joining us today. In Q1, we delivered robust revenue growth of 30% year-over-year, achieved record quarterly operating profit and generated our highest-ever cash flow for a single quarter. As of the end of Q1, we've seen our user perform more than 26 million AI actions to date, up more than 150% since the end of 2024.
